## How to Read This Repo

1. Start with `00_Phase2_Inventory.md`
2. Read sections in numerical order
3. Stop if you are looking for build instructions — they are intentionally absent

---

## Plain‑English Summary

This folder contains theory‑only analysis that finishes the math and logic behind the Lunar Dust Mitigator without authorizing construction or testing. It exists to remove hidden feasibility risks before money or hardware are involved. Nothing in Phase 2 grants permission to build anything.
